data.title: Support the Pauline F. and W. David Robbins Family YMCA
data.text:
The Pauline F. and W. David Robbins Family YMCA, a branch of the YMCA of the Chesapeake, is a 501(c)(3) not-for-profit charitable organization serving the communities of Dorchester County, Maryland. Our cause is strengthening community through programs that build a healthy spirit, mind, and body for all.

Maryland faces new challenges that create a greater need for the work we do. Fortunately, where some see obstacles, we see opportunities for our members, volunteers, staff, and generous donors like you to make a difference.

No other organization can impact as many people as powerfully as we do every day. When you give to the Pauline F. and W. David Robbins Family YMCA, your gift will help young people achieve their potential, empower people of all ages to lead healthier live and strengthen the bonds of community.

Together, weâ€™ll take on many of the greatest challenges facing our young people, our health, and our community.
